  "prompt": "What is the worlds favourite colour?",
  "response": "Determining the \"world's favorite color\" is challenging because preferences can vary greatly across different cultures, regions, and individuals. However, some studies and surveys have been conducted to gauge color preferences on a global scale.\n\nA well-known study by the American paint company Behr, which surveyed people in 12 countries, found that blue was the most favored color overall. Another study published in the journal \"Color Research and Application\" also found that blue was the top choice across various countries.\n\nWhile blue seems to be a popular choice, it's important to note that color preferences can be influenced by many factors, including cultural associations, personal experiences, and current trends. Therefore, while blue may be widely favored, there isn't a single \"world's favorite color\" that applies universally to everyone.",
